  <item rdf:about="2023/1208-lunch/">
            <title>2023/12/08: 麺屋 味方</title>
        <link>https://www.don.to/diary/2023/1208-lunch/</link>
        <description><![CDATA[<p>慈恵会の診察帰りに味方へ。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9438.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9438.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9438.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9438.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9438"/></a></p>

