  <item rdf:about="2023/1125-field/">
            <title>2023/11/25: 芋掘り</title>
        <link>https://www.don.to/diary/2023/1125-field/</link>
        <description><![CDATA[<p>同期にお誘い頂いて娘と一緒に芋掘り(兼BBQ)へ。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9404.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9404.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9404.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9404.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9404"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9405.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9405.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9405.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9405.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9405"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9406.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9406.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9406.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9406.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9406"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9407.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9407.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9407.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9407.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9407"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9408.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9408.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9408.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9408.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9408"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9409.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9409.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9409.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9409.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9409"/></a></p>

<p>生姜とか里芋とかサツマイモとかめっちゃもらう。美味しかった。</p>
]]></description>
        <dc:date>2024-2023-11T00:00:00+09:00</dc:date>

  </item>
  <item rdf:about="2023/1119-horse/">
            <title>2023/11/19: 府中競馬場</title>
        <link>https://www.don.to/diary/2023/1119-horse/</link>
        <description><![CDATA[<p>息子さんが競馬にハマってるので府中競馬場へ(未成年なので賭けてない)。
日本で競馬見るの初めてです。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9394.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9394.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9394.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9394.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9394"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9395.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9395.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9395.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9395.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9395"/></a></p>

<p>席についた後、さっそくパドックへ。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9396.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9396.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9396.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9396.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9396"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_4410.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_4410.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_4410.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_4410.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_4410"/></a></p>

<p>さっぱり分からんので<a href="https://www.jra.go.jp/facilities/race/tokyo/restaurant/pdf/20240122-tenpo.pdf">グルメマップ</a>を見ながらG1焼きでモツ煮込みを買いに行く。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9397.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9397.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9397.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9397.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9397"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9398.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9398.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9398.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9398.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9398"/></a></p>

<p>息子さんはレースとパドックの往復でめっちゃ忙しい。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_4412.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_4412.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_4412.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_4412.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_4412"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_4413.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_4413.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_4413.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_4413.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_4413"/></a></p>

<p>あたしゃ、レースが終わるとツマミを買いに行くのでめっちゃ忙しい。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9399.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9399.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9399.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9399.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9399"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9400.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9400.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9400.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9400.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9400"/></a></p>
]]></description>
        <dc:date>2024-2023-11T00:00:00+09:00</dc:date>

  </item>
  <item rdf:about="2023/1111-camp/">
