  <item rdf:about="2023/1002-seattle/">
            <title>2023/10/02: シアトル出張 その1</title>
        <link>https://www.don.to/diary/2023/1002-seattle/</link>
        <description><![CDATA[<p>久しぶりのシアトル出張。入国審査は長蛇の列。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9194.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9194.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9194.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9194.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9194"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9195.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9195.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9195.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9195.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9195"/></a></p>

<p>電車でダウンタウンへ移動。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9196.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9196.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9196.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9196.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9196"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9197.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9197.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9197.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9197.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9197"/></a></p>

<p>今回のホテル。</p>

<pre class="address">
<a href="https://www.hyatt.com/hyatt-regency/ja-JP/sears-hyatt-regency-seattle">Hyatt Regency Seattle</a>
808 Howell Street, Seattle, Washington, United States, 98101
+1 206 973 1234
</pre>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9198.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9198.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9198.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9198.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9198"/></a></p>

<p>現地の同僚たちと飲む。</p>

<pre class="address">
<a href="https://www.elysianbrewing.com/locations/capitol-hill">Elysian Capitol Hill Brewery</a>
1221 Pike Street Seattle, WA 98122
</pre>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9200.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9200.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9200.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9200.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9200"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9201.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9201.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9201.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9201.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9201"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9202.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9202.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9202.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9202.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9202"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9203.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9203.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9203.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9203.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9203"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9204.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9204.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9204.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9204.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9204"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9205.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9205.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9205.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9205.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9205"/></a></p>
